Program: The Why Factor
Title: Self-Marriage
Link: https://www.bbc.co.uk/programmes/w3cswrjx
Last Broadcast Date: Mon 21 May 2018
Why do people marry themselves – and what even is self-marriage? The Why Factor meets the self-married, who argue if marriage is about committing to an individual - to love and cherish, in sickness and in health - who better to commit to… than yourself? Mary-Ann Ochota finds out why this emerging phenomenon is so popular amongst women in particular. And why self-marriage can be either a radical act of self-love, or the ultimate cosplay. And sometimes both. (Image: Grace Gelder, Credit: Amy Grubb) Show less